funny games is a 2007 psychological thriller film written and directed by michael haneke , and a remake of his own 1997 austrian film of the same name . naomi watts , tim roth , michael pitt , and brady corbet star in the main roles . the film is a shot-for-shot remake of the 1997 film , albeit in english and set in the united states with different actors . exterior scenes were filmed on long island . the film is an international co-production of the united states , united kingdom , france , germany , and italy . haneke has stated that the film is a reflection and criticism of violence used in media .